# VitalWatch — Architecture Diagram

## High-Level System Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Client Layer"
        WEB["🌐 React Web App<br/>(Vite + TypeScript)"]
        APK["📱 Android APK<br/>(Capacitor)"]
    end

    subgraph "Frontend Application"
        direction TB
        ROUTER["React Router<br/>(BrowserRouter)"]
        AUTH["Auth Guard<br/>(RequireAuth)"]
        
        subgraph "Pages"
            IDX["Landing Page<br/>(Index)"]
            LOGIN["Login Page<br/>(Doctor / Patient)"]
            DOC["Doctor Dashboard"]
            PAT["Patient Portal"]
        end
    end

    subgraph "Backend Services"
        SUPA_DB["🗄️ Supabase<br/>PostgreSQL Database"]
        SUPA_RT["⚡ Supabase<br/>Realtime Broadcast"]
        ML_SRV["🧠 Flask ML Server<br/>(localhost:5000)"]
    end

    WEB --> ROUTER
    APK --> ROUTER
    ROUTER --> AUTH
    AUTH --> IDX
    AUTH --> LOGIN
    AUTH --> DOC
    AUTH --> PAT

    DOC <--> SUPA_RT
    PAT <--> SUPA_RT
    DOC --> SUPA_DB
    PAT --> SUPA_DB
    DOC --> ML_SRV

    style WEB fill:#1a1a2e,stroke:#6366f1,color:#e0e0ff
    style APK fill:#1a1a2e,stroke:#6366f1,color:#e0e0ff
    style SUPA_DB fill:#1a2e1a,stroke:#22c55e,color:#e0ffe0
    style SUPA_RT fill:#1a2e1a,stroke:#22c55e,color:#e0ffe0
    style ML_SRV fill:#2e1a1a,stroke:#ef4444,color:#ffe0e0
```

