## Data Flow Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph "Patient Device"
        PS["Patient Portal"]
        VG["Vitals Generator<br/>(mockData.ts)"]
    end

    subgraph "Supabase Cloud"
        BC["Realtime Broadcast<br/>Channel: vitals-{roomCode}"]
        DB["PostgreSQL<br/>rooms table"]
    end

    subgraph "Doctor Device"
        DD["Doctor Dashboard"]
        ML_LOCAL["Browser ML Engine<br/>(mlEngine.ts)"]
    end

    subgraph "Local ML Server"
        FLASK["Flask API<br/>:5000"]
        MODELS["Scikit-Learn Models<br/>RF · GBR · IF · ETR"]
    end

    VG -->|"2.5s interval"| PS
    PS -->|"sendVitals()"| BC
    BC -->|"subscribeToVitals()"| DD
    DD -->|"vitals history"| ML_LOCAL
    DD -->|"POST /api/analyze"| FLASK
    FLASK --> MODELS
    PS -->|"createRoom / validateRoom"| DB
    DD -->|"createRoom / validateRoom"| DB

    style BC fill:#1a2e1a,stroke:#22c55e,color:#e0ffe0
    style DB fill:#1a2e1a,stroke:#22c55e,color:#e0ffe0
    style FLASK fill:#2e1a1a,stroke:#ef4444,color:#ffe0e0
    style MODELS fill:#2e1a1a,stroke:#ef4444,color:#ffe0e0
    style ML_LOCAL fill:#1a1a2e,stroke:#a78bfa,color:#e0e0ff
```

