## ML Pipeline Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph "Browser ML Engine (mlEngine.ts)"
        direction TB
        IN1["Input: Vital Histories"]
        DA["detectAnomalies()<br/>Z-Score Analysis"]
        PT["predictTrends()<br/>Linear Regression"]
        DP["detectPatterns()<br/>Clinical Rules"]
        RS["computeMLRiskScore()<br/>NEWS2 + Weighted"]
        GI["generateInsights()<br/>Human-Readable"]
        N2["computeNEWS2()<br/>Clinical Scoring"]
    end

    subgraph "Flask ML Server (ml_model.py)"
        direction TB
        IN2["Input: Raw Vitals + History"]
        RF["RandomForestClassifier<br/>(100 trees, depth=12)"]
        GB["GradientBoostingRegressor<br/>(150 trees, lr=0.1)"]
        IF["IsolationForest<br/>(contamination=0.1)"]
        ET["ExtraTreesRegressor<br/>(80 trees, depth=8)"]
        FA["full_analysis()<br/>Risk + Anomalies + Trends + Patterns"]
    end

    IN1 --> DA & PT & DP
    DA & PT & DP --> RS
    RS --> GI
    IN1 --> N2

    IN2 --> RF & GB & IF & ET
    RF & GB & IF & ET --> FA

    style DA fill:#7c3aed,stroke:#a78bfa,color:#fff
    style PT fill:#7c3aed,stroke:#a78bfa,color:#fff
    style DP fill:#7c3aed,stroke:#a78bfa,color:#fff
    style RF fill:#dc2626,stroke:#f87171,color:#fff
    style GB fill:#dc2626,stroke:#f87171,color:#fff
    style IF fill:#dc2626,stroke:#f87171,color:#fff
    style ET fill:#dc2626,stroke:#f87171,color:#fff
```

