## Realtime Room System

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Doctor
    participant S as Supabase
    participant P as Patient

    D->>S: createRoom(doctorName)
    S-->>D: roomCode (6-digit)
    D->>S: subscribeToVitals(roomCode)

    P->>S: validateRoom(roomCode)
    S-->>P: ✅ Active
    P->>S: announceJoin(channel, name)
    S-->>D: 🔔 patient_join event

    loop Every 2.5 seconds
        P->>S: sendVitals(channel, vitals)
        S-->>D: 📊 vitals event
    end

    P->>S: announceLeave(channel, name)
    S-->>D: 👋 patient_leave event
    D->>S: closeRoom(roomCode)
```

---

## Tech Stack Summary

| Layer | Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| **Frontend** | React 18 + TypeScript | UI framework |
| **Bundler** | Vite 5 | Dev server & build |
| **Styling** | TailwindCSS 3 | Utility-first CSS |
| **UI Library** | shadcn/ui (Radix) | Component primitives |
| **Charts** | Recharts | Vital sign graphs |
| **State** | TanStack React Query | Server state |
| **Routing** | React Router 6 | Client-side nav |
| **Auth** | localStorage sessions | Demo auth |
| **Database** | Supabase (PostgreSQL) | Room persistence |
| **Realtime** | Supabase Broadcast | Live vitals streaming |
| **Browser ML** | Custom TS engine | Anomaly, trend, pattern, NEWS2 |
| **Server ML** | Flask + scikit-learn | RF, GBR, IF, ETR models |
| **Mobile** | Capacitor 8 | Android APK wrapper |
| **Testing** | Vitest + Testing Library | Unit tests |
